---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="문의 — BSVibe" description="BSVibe 팀에 문의하세요" locale="ko">
  <div class="contact-page">
    <header class="contact-hero">
      <h1>문의하기</h1>
      <p class="lead">제품, 협력, 채용에 대한 모든 문의를 환영합니다.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📧</div>
        <h2>이메일</h2>
        <p>가장 빠른 응답을 위해 이메일로 문의해 주세요.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@bsvibe.dev" class="contact-link">contact@bsvibe.dev</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">💼</div>
        <h2>비즈니스</h2>
        <p>엔터프라이즈 플랜, 파트너십, 컨설팅 문의.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@bsvibe.dev?subject=비즈니스 문의" class="contact-link">비즈니스 문의 보내기 →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🐛</div>
        <h2>버그 신고</h2>
        <p>발견한 문제를 알려주세요. 빠르게 수정하겠습니다.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@bsvibe.dev?subject=버그 신고" class="contact-link">버그 신고하기 →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">💡</div>
        <h2>피드백</h2>
        <p>제품에 대한 의견과 제안을 들려주세요.</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@bsvibe.dev?subject=피드백" class="contact-link">피드백 보내기 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info">
      <h2>다른 채널</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>GitHub</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/BSVibe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/BSVibe</a></li>
        <li><strong>응답 시간</strong>: 평일 24시간 이내</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 16px 24px 120px;
  }
  .contact-hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .contact-hero h1 {
    color: #f2f3f7;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .contact-hero .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #8187a8;
  }
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .contact-card {
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #2a2d42;
    background-color: #111218;
  }
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .contact-card h2 {
    color: #f2f3f7;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .contact-card p {
    color: #8187a8;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .contact-link {
    color: #818cf8;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-link:hover {
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }
  .contact-info {
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #1e2033;
    background-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.04);
  }
  .contact-info h2 {
    color: #f2f3f7;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .contact-info ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .contact-info li {
    color: #a8adc6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .contact-info strong {
    color: #e4e6ee;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .contact-info a {
    color: #818cf8;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
